---
title: Chicken Sausage & Pepper Upside Down Pizza with Pillsbury™️ Original Crescent Rolls & Garlic Butter
description: This super-simple weeknight dinner idea is about to turn your world upside-down—literally! It’s crust-on-top pizza! Here’s how you make it: sauté hearty, savory chicken sausage and bell peppers, stir in marinara sauce, add mozzarella and Parmesan, then top with premade crescent roll dough (mmm…flaky goodness!). Bake it all to bubbly, golden perfection, then brush with savory garlic butter, and in just 25 minutes, you’ll be serving it up like a kitchen hero!
